snippet.title: Megapak Volume 1 | Atari Lynx Collection 1 | Game 11 of 17 | Evercade Handheld
snippet.description:
An amazing collection of mini-games including ChopperX, Parafly, Password, High Roller, Blackjack, Sketch and Soundtool.

There might be more games on this cartridge than are "officially" listed. You'll have to do a little bit of searching though!

Year: 2008
Publisher: Songbird Productions
Genre: Miscellaneous
